", "bbox": [354.8, 320.9, 391.5, 340.1]}, {"text": "30  $", "bbox": [433.6, 320.9, 483.3, 340.1]}, {"text": "66", "bbox": [517.1, 320.9, 556.6, 340.1]}, {"text": "108", "bbox": [590.3, 320.9, 615.4, 339.3]}, {"text": "Fair value of contracts", "bbox": [71.3, 339.3, 224.9, 357.7]}, {"text": "outstanding at the", "bbox": [78.8, 355.9, 201.5, 374.4]}, {"text": "end of the period", "bbox": [78.8, 372.6, 200.6, 391.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [227.3, 372.7, 239.9, 391.1]}, {"text": "362  $", "bbox": [265.3, 372.0, 321.1, 391.1]}, {"text": "749  $", "bbox": [346.5, 372.0, 399.9, 391.1]}, {"text": "103  $", "bbox": [425.3, 372.0, 483.3, 391.1]}, {"text": "66  $", "bbox": [517.1, 372.0, 560.8, 391.1]}, {"text": "1,280", "bbox": [577.8, 372.0, 615.4, 390.4]}, {"text": "PPL sells electricity, capacity and related services and buys fuel", "bbox": [71.3, 419.9, 610.4, 443.0]}, {"text": "on a forward basis to hedge the value of energy from its", "bbox": [71.3, 443.9, 542.3, 467.0]}, {"text": "generation assets.  If PPL were unable to deliver firm capacity", "bbox": [71.3, 467.8, 596.0, 490.9]}, {"text": "and energy or to accept the delivery of fuel under its agreements,", "bbox": [71.3, 491.8, 618.1, 514.9]}, {"text": "under certain circumstances it could be required to pay", "bbox": [71.3, 515.8, 533.8, 539.0]}, {"text": "liquidating damages.  These damages would be based on the", "bbox": [71.3, 539.7, 580.1, 562.8]}, {"text": "difference between the market price and the contract price of the", "bbox": [71.3, 563.7, 614.9, 586.9]}, {"text": "commodity.  Depending on price changes in the wholesale", "bbox": [71.3, 587.8, 564.5, 610.9]}, {"text": "energy markets, such damages could be significant.  Extreme", "bbox": [71.3, 611.6, 587.0, 634.8]}, {"text": "weather conditions, unplanned power plant outages,", "bbox": [71.3, 635.7, 510.2, 658.8]}, {"text": "transmission disruptions, nonperformance by counterparties (or", "bbox": [71.3, 659.7, 605.7, 682.8]}, {"text": "their own counterparties) with which it has energy contracts and", "bbox": [71.3, 683.6, 612.0, 706.7]}, {"text": "other factors could affect PPL's ability to meet its obligations, or", "bbox": [71.3, 707.6, 614.8, 730.7]}, {"text": "cause significant increases in the market price of replacement", "bbox": [71.3, 731.6, 589.4, 754.7]}, {"text": "energy.  Although PPL attempts to mitigate these risks, there can", "bbox": [71.3, 755.5, 618.4, 778.6]}, {"text": "be no assurance that it will be able to fully meet its firm", "bbox": [71.3, 779.5, 542.1, 802.6]}, {"text": "obligations, that it will not be required to pay damages for", "bbox": [71.3, 803.5, 561.2, 826.6]}, {"text": "failure to perform, or that it will not experience counterparty", "bbox": [71.3, 827.4, 581.2, 850.5]}, {"text": "nonperformance in the future.", "bbox": [71.3, 851.4, 325.3, 874.5]}, {"text": "Commodity Price Risk (Trading)", "bbox": [71.3, 899.3, 350.2, 922.4]}, {"text": "PPL's trading contracts mature at various times through", "bbox": [71.3, 947.2, 539.5, 970.3]}, {"text": "2015.  The following table sets forth changes in the net fair value", "bbox": [71.3, 971.2, 620.2, 994.3]}, {"text": "of PPL's trading commodity derivative contracts.  See Notes 17", "bbox": [71.3, 995.2, 605.9, 1018.4]}, {"text": "and 18 to the Financial Statements for additional information.", "bbox": [71.3, 1019.1, 591.3, 1042.2]}, {"text": "Gains (Losses)", "bbox": [471.3, 1065.0, 578.7, 1083.4]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [450.3, 1082.6, 488.0, 1101.1]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [562.5, 1082.6, 600.1, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Fair value of contracts outstanding at the", "bbox": [71.3, 1111.5, 347.7, 1129.9]}, {"text": "beginning of the period", "bbox": [78.8, 1130.7, 239.0, 1149.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [407.0, 1131.4, 431.8, 1149.8]}, {"text": "(75)  $", "bbox": [484.2, 1130.7, 540.1, 1149.8]}, {"text": "16", "bbox": [603.1, 1130.7, 619.8, 1149.1]}, {"text": "Contracts realized or otherwise settled during the", "bbox": [71.3, 1149.9, 