ading", "bbox": [652.8, 779.5, 1196.2, 802.6]}, {"text": "VAR exposure is expected to be limited in the short term.  At", "bbox": [652.8, 803.5, 1170.6, 826.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009 and December 31, 2008, the VaR for PPL's", "bbox": [652.8, 827.4, 1187.9, 850.5]}, {"text": "portfolios using end-of-quarter results for the period was as", "bbox": [652.8, 851.4, 1153.6, 874.5]}, {"text": "follows.", "bbox": [652.8, 875.3, 726.0, 898.4]}, {"text": "Trading VaR", "bbox": [903.9, 923.4, 1002.9, 941.8]}, {"text": "Non-Trading VaR", "bbox": [1054.7, 923.4, 1189.0, 941.8]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [895.3, 943.5, 932.9, 961.9]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [978.9, 943.5, 1016.6, 961.9]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [1060.8, 943.5, 1098.5, 961.9]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [1145.2, 943.5, 1181.2, 961.9]}, {"text": "95% Confidence Level,", "bbox": [652.8, 963.4, 818.7, 981.8]}, {"text": "Five-Day Holding Period", "bbox": [660.3, 982.5, 834.0, 1000.9]}, {"text": "Period End", "bbox": [675.3, 1001.7, 754.0, 1020.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [873.1, 1001.7, 885.6, 1020.2]}, {"text": "3  $", "bbox": [936.2, 1001.7, 974.0, 1020.2]}, {"text": "3  $", "bbox": [1015.0, 1001.7, 1049.4, 1020.2]}, {"text": "8  $", "bbox": [1099.2, 1001.7, 1132.0, 1020.2]}, {"text": "10", "bbox": [1175.3, 1001.7, 1192.0, 1020.2]}, {"text": "Average for the Period", "bbox": [675.3, 1020.9, 831.8, 1039.3]}, {"text": "4", "bbox": [936.1, 1020.9, 965.5, 1039.3]}, {"text": "10", "bbox": [1006.5, 1020.9, 1045.2, 1039.3]}, {"text": "9", "bbox": [1099.2, 1020.9, 1127.7, 1039.3]}, {"text": "14", "bbox": [1175.2, 1020.9, 1191.9, 1039.3]}, {"text": "High", "bbox": [675.3, 1040.0, 712.9, 1058.4]}, {"text": "8", "bbox": [936.2, 1040.0, 965.6, 1058.4]}, {"text": "22", "bbox": [1006.6, 1040.0, 1045.3, 1058.4]}, {"text": "11", "bbox": [1090.9, 1040.0, 1127.8, 1058.4]}, {"text": "20", "bbox": [1175.3, 1040.0, 1192.0, 1058.4]}, {"text": "Low", "bbox": [675.3, 1059.3, 709.9, 1077.7]}, {"text": "1", "bbox": [936.1, 1059.3, 9